title: Wasteland 022 (2008) (c2c) (GreenGiant-DCP)
description:
Wasteland 022 (2008) (c2c) (GreenGiant-DCP)

by Antony Johnston, Chris Mitten & Chuck BB
Captured by the Red Fangs Dog Tribe, Michael and Abi are helpless. But aid can come in strange forms. Who is the mysterious man so interested in their welfare? What does it have to do with an impending marriage? And who will come from the city to save them?

Thanks to GreenGiant
